 "cells": [
  {
   "metadata": {},
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "source": [
    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"# Project 88 \\u2014 Local Audio Transcription + Summary\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"**Transcribe local audio with Whisper and summarize with Ollama.**\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| Component | Choice |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"|-----------|--------|\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| STT | OpenAI Whisper (local) |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| LLM | Ollama (qwen3:8b) |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| Fallback | Pre-written transcript |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| Interface | Jupyter |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"> **Note:** Requires `openai-whisper` package and ffmpeg. Falls back to\\n\",\n",
    "    \"> a sample transcript if Whisper is not installed.\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 1 \\u00b7 What You Will Learn\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"1. Use **Whisper locally** for speech-to-text\\n\",\n",
    "    \"2. **Summarize transcripts** with a local LLM\\n\",\n",
    "    \"3. Extract **action items** from meetings\\n\",\n",
    "    \"4. Handle **fallback** when audio tools are unavailable\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 2 \\u00b7 Setup\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"# !pip install -q langchain langchain-ollama\\n\",\n",
    "    \"# !pip install -q openai-whisper  # optional, needs ffmpeg\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 3 \\u00b7 Imports\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"import json\\n\",\n",
    "    \"from langchain_ollama import ChatOllama\\n\",\n",
    "    \"from langchain_core.prompts import ChatPromptTemplate\\n\",\n",
    "    \"from langchain_core.output_parsers import StrOutputParser\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"MODEL = 'qwen3:8b'\\n\",\n",
    "    \"llm = ChatOllama(model=MODEL, temperature=0.2)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"try:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    import whisper\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    WHISPER_AVAILABLE = True\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    print(f'Whisper available. LLM: {MODEL}')\\n\",\n",
    "    \"except ImportError:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    WHISPER_AVAILABLE = False\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    print(f'Whisper not installed, using sample transcript. LLM: {MODEL}')\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 4 \\u00b7 Transcribe Audio\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"If Whisper is available and you have an audio file, it transcribes locally.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Otherwise, we use a realistic sample transcript.\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"SAMPLE_TRANSCRIPT = \\\"\\\"\\\"Okay, let's get started with the weekly standup.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Sarah: Last week I finished the API integration with the payment provider.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"This week I'm working on the webhook handlers for subscription events.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Blocker: I need access to the staging payment sandbox.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Mike: I completed the dashboard redesign mockups. Got feedback from\\nthe product team, making revisions. No blockers.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Lisa: I've been debugging the memory leak in the background worker.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Found the issue - unclosed database connections in the batch processor.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Fix is in PR #234, needs review.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Manager: Great progress. Sarah, I'll get you sandbox access today.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Lisa, can Mike review your PR? Let's also discuss the Q2 roadmap\\n\",\n",
    "    \"in Thursday's planning session. Action items: sandbox access for Sarah,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"PR review for Lisa, Q2 roadmap prep for Thursday.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"if WHISPER_AVAILABLE:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    import os\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    audio_file = 'meeting.wav'  # replace with your audio file\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    if os.path.exists(audio_file):\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        model = whisper.load_model('base')\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        result = model.transcribe(audio_file)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        transcript = result['text']\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        print(f'Transcribed {len(transcript)} chars from {audio_file}')\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    else:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        transcript = SAMPLE_TRANSCRIPT\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        print(f'No audio file found, using sample ({len(transcript)} chars)')\\n\",\n",
    "    \"else:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    transcript = SAMPLE_TRANSCRIPT\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    print(f'Using sample transcript ({len(transcript)} chars)')\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f'\\\\nFirst 200 chars:\\\\n{transcript[:200]}...')\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 5 \\u00b7 Summarize\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"summary_prompt = ChatPromptTemplate.from_messages([\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    ('system', 'Summarize this meeting transcript. Include: key decisions, updates, and blockers.'),\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    ('human', '{transcript}'),\\n\",\n",
    "    \"])\\n\",\n",
    "    \"summary = (summary_prompt | llm | StrOutputParser()).invoke({'transcript': transcript})\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print('SUMMARY:')\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(summary)\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 6 \\u00b7 Extract Action Items\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"action_prompt = ChatPromptTemplate.from_messages([\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    ('system', 'Extract action items from this transcript. Return JSON array: [{\\\"owner\\\": \\\"...\\\", \\\"action\\\": \\\"...\\\", \\\"deadline\\\": \\\"...\\\"}]'),\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    ('human', '{transcript}'),\\n\",\n",
    "    \"])\\n\",\n",
    "    \"raw = (action_prompt | llm | StrOutputParser()).invoke({'transcript': transcript})\\n\",\n",
    "    \"try:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    s, e = raw.find('['), raw.rfind(']') + 1\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    actions = json.loads(raw[s:e]) if s >= 0 else []\\n\",\n",
    "    \"except: actions = []\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print('ACTION ITEMS:')\\n\",\n",
    "    \"for a in actions:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    print(f'  [{a.get(\\\"owner\\\",\\\"?\\\")}] {a.get(\\\"action\\\",\\\"?\\\")} (by: {a.get(\\\"deadline\\\",\\\"TBD\\\")})')\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 7 \\u00b7 Export\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"output = {'transcript': transcript, 'summary': summary, 'actions': actions}\\n\",\n",
    "    \"with open('meeting_summary.json', 'w') as f: json.dump(output, f, indent=2, default=str)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print('Saved.')\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 8 \\u00b7 Key Takeaways\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- Whisper runs fully local for private audio transcription\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- LLM summarization extracts key decisions and blockers\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- Action item extraction structures follow-up tasks\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- Fallback transcripts keep the notebook useful without audio hardware\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  }\n",
    " ],\n",
